* {{audio|en-us-civil.ogg|Audio (US)|lang=en}}
* {{rhymes|ɪvəl|lang=en}}

===Adjective===
{{en-adj}}

# {{lb|en|uncomparable}} Having to do with people and [[government]] office as opposed to the military or religion.
#: ''She went into '''civil''' service because she wanted to help the people.''
